## Quick Reference

### Commands
- `/delegate` - Start new delegation session
- `/delegate <task>` - Start with specific task
- `/sync` - Review and merge agents
- `/sync --status` - Check status only
- `/sync --abort` - Cancel session

### Agent States
```
PENDING    → Waiting to be spawned
SPAWNING   → Creation in progress
RUNNING    → Actively working
CHECKPOINT → Awaiting review
COMPLETE   → Finished successfully
FAILED     → Encountered error
MERGED     → Integrated into main
ABORTED    → Cancelled
```

### Merge Flow
```
1. Agent completes subtask
2. /sync shows in "Ready to Merge"
3. Human reviews changes
4. Human approves merge
5. Changes integrated
6. Tests run
7. Agent marked MERGED
```
